These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, russian, thai, turkish
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the turkish is between the german and the russian##2
3. the turkish is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german | turkish | russian | thai |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, banana, lemon, potato
1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | banana | avocado | potato | lemon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, martial-arts, mystery, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | mystery | martial-arts |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, snowboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | snowboarding | baseball | weightlifting | soccer |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | water-polo | handball | sailing | lacrosse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, colombian, thai
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the thai##3
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian | thai | chinese |

