1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | scooter | roller | van | jet-ski |

