2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting | biathlon | rugby |

