.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peach, pineapple, strawberry
1. the person eating peach is the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating pineapple is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | pineapple | strawberry | peach | avocado |

